text: The Alamo Fire was a wildfire in San Luis Obispo County, California. The fire started on July 6, 2017 at 3:44 PM and destroyed 28,687 acres. The fire was near the Twitchell Reservoir. It was fully contained on 19 July 2017. The fire destroyed one house and one structure. The cause is still being investigated. == References == Category:2017 California wildfires Category:2017 in weather Category:July 2017 events
title: Alamo Fire (2017)
